 />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5b59b4ec1c342f94811ecae5da13ec9ea25ab27","tid":1631540,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"佢撞向人群 係恐襲行為啊<br />\n煲撚大佢<br />\n<br />\n幾年前法國就係咁"},{"pid":"d0d71529fb3ead6f5f834c21bf4f1688deebd1c4","tid":1631540,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"走唔甩咩?<br />\n次撚次撞完人 斬完人都走得甩架喎<br />\n都有阻膠保護架喎"},{"pid":"eee787128cbe5fb896c4a325e918e016114b90f2","tid":1631540,"uid":111493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"當年羅白頭神風敢死隊咁<br />\n可惜佢應該撞入禮賓府中聯辦先岩"},{"pid":"edeb76d2922e5ba63f8eb22c8189f2957a67b0a9","tid":1631540,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"手足斷腳,佢仲行得走得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n告又告佢唔到,要佢比全香港人杯葛,住係香港生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5050abb0246fb3611701096f523642d7744727","tid":1631540,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94a2247c7b3afe1b2221c0daa32bf5701b1eeba9","tid":1631540,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ff5fc584a04b110adf5972b801f22d369a07681","tid":1631540,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"明知走唔甩、會俾人打死，都單人直衝入人群。<